Using Clustering Techniques to Explore Theft Incidents from the Dallas Crime Dataset¶

MSDS 7331 Data Mining Project 3¶

By Jean Jecha, Sharon Teo, Jessica Wheeler¶

Introduction¶

From exploratory data analysis to using logistic regression, SVMs, gradient-based optomization, and various classification techniques, we have uncovered a lot of information from the Dallas Crime dataset. As mentioned in the previous projects, the Dallas Crime dataset consists of 196k rows in 102 attributes. We continue to narrow down the dataset and use incidents that occurred in 2016 as it contains the most complete data.

We took a closer look at theft incidents as one of our tasks for Project 2. Theft is an interesting subject in regards to this dataset as it was the highest occurring incident in Dallas in 2016. In Project 2, using logistic regression, we had found that the variables disp_clear_time_m, IsDrugRelated, Watch_3, ComplainantRace_B, IsGangRelated, and Division_SouthEast were all negative indicators of our response variable, IsTheft. On the other hand, Hour, Watch_1, ComplainantRace_L, ComplainantRace_W, and rec_disp_time were all positive indicators of theft.

Now we will explore how theft incidents cluster with certain variables and try to attain the most accurate clustering for our dataset. We use classic clustering techniques such as k-means, hierarchical agglomerative clustering, and DBSCAN. We also use the kmodes method of clustering which clusters categorical data. Lastly, we used bubblemap to cluster theft incidents by location.

Loading, Cleaning, and Preprossessing the Data¶

After importing the neccessary packages and reading in the dataset, we cleaned the attribute titles and susbetted the data to include only incidents that occurred in 2016. Since there are so many attributes in this dataset, we chose a sample of variables to keep based on our interests for analysis. Specifically, we wanted to examine the following:

  • Are theft incidents drug or gang related?
  • How do theft incidents cluster with time-related attributes such as the recorded dispatch time? How about the time it takes to clear? What about the days of the week, and more specifically, the weekend?
  • Are there certain areas or locations that get targeted more heavily than others?
  • In regards to the complainant, does gender, race, or age have any clustering effect on theft?

The only information in the dataset about victims is VictimCondition, which isn't exacly relevant to what we are looking at since it applies more to violent crimes. Since we do not have more specific information about the victim, we use the complainant information for analysis. This may still give us good information as to who the targets of theft were. Usually, a person reports a theft incident when something of their own was stolen and/or broken into. Thus, we use information about the complainant to see what kinds of people are getting targeted and if there is any pattern.

In the code below, we converted CallReceivedDateTime, CallClearedDateTime, and CallDispatchDateTime into datetime type attributes. We created the variables rec_disp_time_m and disp_clear_time_m to describe the amount of time between when a call was received to the time officers were dispatched, and dispatch time to when the call was marked as clear, respectively. For theft incidents, clear time is usually when the items were found or recovered. We predict that this variable may cluster well with theft. Next we made sure that these variables only included positive values.

We converted Time1ofOccurrence into a variable called Hour to describe the hour of the day the incident occurred. We also made DrugRelatedIncident and GangRelatedIncident more usefuly by one-hot encoding them into the variables IsDrugRelated and IsGangRelated. Lastly, we created a variable called IsWeekend that represents if an incident occurred on a Friday or Saturday.

# Import Crime data set
# Orginal dataset from https://www.dallasopendata.com/Public-Safety/Police-Incidents/tbnj-w5hb
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import seaborn as sns
%matplotlib inline
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from __future__ import print_function

# read in the csv file
df = pd.read_csv('/Users/sharonteo/Downloads/Police_Incidents.csv')

# Reference: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/11346283/renaming-columns-in-pandas
# Removing spaces from headers

df.columns = [x.strip().replace(' ', '') for x in df.columns]
df.columns = [x.strip().replace('/', '') for x in df.columns]
df.columns = [x.strip().replace('(', '') for x in df.columns]
df.columns = [x.strip().replace(')', '') for x in df.columns]
df.columns = [x.strip().replace('-', '') for x in df.columns]

#df.head()
# Subset the dataset to year 2016
# Ref: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/18172851/deleting-dataframe-row-in-pandas-based-on-column-value

df = df[df.Year1ofOccurrence == 2016]
df = df[df.ComplainantRace != 'TEST']
df = df[df.ComplainantGender != 'TEST']
#list(df)

df_theft = df[['CallReceivedDateTime','CallClearedDateTime','CallDispatchDateTime',
               'Time1ofOccurrence','DrugRelatedIncident','Watch','Month1ofOccurence',
               'ComplainantRace','ComplainantGender','ComplainantAge','Division',
               'Day1oftheWeek','GangRelatedOffense','UCROffenseDescription','XCoordinate',
               'YCoordinate']].copy()

df_theft['CallReceivedDateTime'] = pd.to_datetime(df_theft['CallReceivedDateTime'])
df_theft['CallClearedDateTime'] = pd.to_datetime(df_theft['CallClearedDateTime'])
df_theft['CallDispatchDateTime'] = pd.to_datetime(df_theft['CallDispatchDateTime'])
        
# Compute the time between call received and call displatched, call Displatch and call cleared.
# Reference: http://www.itgo.me/a/x791470639852744898/calculate-pandas-dataframe-time-difference-between-two-columns-in-hours-and-minu
df_theft['rec_disp_time_m'] = (df_theft['CallDispatchDateTime'] - df_theft['CallReceivedDateTime']).astype('timedelta64[m]')
df_theft['disp_clear_time_m'] = (df_theft['CallClearedDateTime'] - df_theft['CallDispatchDateTime']).astype('timedelta64[m]')

# Remove rows with negative time difference
df_theft = df_theft[df_theft.rec_disp_time_m >= 0]
df_theft = df_theft[df_theft.disp_clear_time_m >= 0]

# Create Hour of Occurrence from Time Occurrence 
# Ref: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/25789445/pandas-make-new-column-from-string-slice-of-another-column
df_theft['Hour'] = df_theft.Time1ofOccurrence.str[:2]
df_theft['Hour'] = (df_theft['Hour']).astype('float64')

# change Drug Related attribute to a more usable value
df_theft['IsDrugRelated'] = df_theft.DrugRelatedIncident == 'Yes'
df_theft.IsDrugRelated = df_theft.IsDrugRelated.astype(np.int)

# change Gang Related attribute to a more usable value
df_theft['IsGangRelated'] = df_theft.GangRelatedOffense == 'Yes'
df_theft.IsGangRelated = df_theft.IsGangRelated.astype(np.int)

# Change day of week to indicate weekend   
df_theft['IsWeekend'] = (df_theft['Day1oftheWeek'] == 'Sat') | (df_theft['Day1oftheWeek'] == 'Fri') 
df_theft.IsWeekend = df_theft.IsWeekend.astype(np.int)

# Remove call datetime call columns
for col in ['CallReceivedDateTime','CallClearedDateTime','CallDispatchDateTime',
            'Time1ofOccurrence','Day1oftheWeek','GangRelatedOffense']:
    if col in df_theft:
        del df_theft[col]

Imputing the variables¶

We imputed the dataset using group medians. For the attributes ComplainantRace, ComplainantGender, and Division, any NAs were filled using the highest occurring values. The complainant's age variable was separated according to an age range in ComplainantAgeRange.

In [2]:
# creating missing values (imputing) grouping by day of week and watch
df_grouped = df_theft.groupby(by=['Month1ofOccurence','Watch'])

# Using grouping to impute data in each group and then transform back 
# Impute missing numerical values 
df_imputed = df_grouped.transform(lambda grp: grp.fillna(grp.median()))

# Impute missing categorical values
# Ref: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/32617811/imputation-of-missing-values-for-categories-in-pandas

# Impute missing values for complainant race
df_imputed['ComplainantRace'] = df_grouped.ComplainantRace.fillna(df_theft['ComplainantRace'].value_counts().index[0])

# Impute missing values for complainant gender
df_imputed['ComplainantGender'] = df_grouped.ComplainantGender.fillna(df_theft['ComplainantGender'].value_counts().index[0])

# Impute missing values for Division
df_imputed['Division'] = df_grouped.Division.fillna(df_theft['Division'].value_counts().index[0])

# break age into groups 
df_imputed['ComplainantAgeRange'] = pd.cut(df_imputed.ComplainantAge,[0,16,24,65,1e6],4,labels=[0,1,2,3])
df_imputed['ComplainantAgeRange'] = (df_imputed['ComplainantAgeRange']).astype('int64')

# Filling the grouped variables from original data frame
df_imputed[['Month1ofOccurence','Watch','UCROffenseDescription','DrugRelatedIncident']] = df_theft[['Month1ofOccurence','Watch','UCROffenseDescription','DrugRelatedIncident']]

# Create imputed file for KMode analysis
df_imputed_KMode = df_imputed[['ComplainantAgeRange','ComplainantAge','ComplainantRace',
                      'ComplainantGender','Division','Watch','UCROffenseDescription',
                      'Hour','IsDrugRelated']].copy()

# Plot data for all
df_Plot = df_imputed[['XCoordinate','YCoordinate']].copy()

# Plot data for Theft only
tmp_theft = df_imputed[df_imputed.UCROffenseDescription == 'THEFT']
df_Plot_theft = tmp_theft[['XCoordinate','YCoordinate']].copy()

# Plot data for drug related crimes
tmp_drug = df_imputed[df_imputed.DrugRelatedIncident == 'Yes']
df_Plot_drug = tmp_drug[['XCoordinate','YCoordinate']].copy()

# Remove call datetime call columns
for col in ['DrugRelatedIncident']:
    if col in df_imputed:
        del df_imputed[col]

Clustering on Theft¶

To start, we used the StratifiedKFold function from scikit-learn and chose to do 10 splits. This way we can cross-validate the data using training and testing sets. A Random Forest Classifier algorithm is used and the average accuracy of classifying whether an incident is theft or not is shown below. This gives us our baseline classification performance with all of the variables we decided to keep, based on our results from Project 2.

In [21]:
# Response variable of IsTheft
# significant variables from project 2
from sklearn.model_selection import StratifiedKFold, cross_val_score
from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier

y = df_imputed['IsTheft']
X = df_imputed[['Watch_3','Watch_2','Watch_1','Hour','disp_clear_time_m',
                'rec_disp_time_m','ComplainantGender_F','ComplainantGender_M',
                'IsDrugRelated','ComplainantRace_B','ComplainantRace_L',
                'ComplainantRace_W','Division_SouthEast','ComplainantAgeRange',
                'ComplainantAge']]

cv = StratifiedKFold(n_splits=10)

clf = RandomForestClassifier(n_estimators=150,random_state=1)

acc = cross_val_score(clf,X,y=y,cv=cv)

print ("Average accuracy = ", acc.mean()*100, "+-", acc.std()*100)

Average accuracy =  76.483715791 +- 0.705957439256

We can see that the accuracy of this model is about 76.48 with a standard deviation of +/- 0.705. Below we used KMeans clustering with the parameters as shown:

In [23]:
# Reference: "Python Machine Learning by Sebastian Raschka" 
# plot for estimated number of clusters
from matplotlib import pyplot as plt
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans

X=df_imputed[['Watch_3','Watch_2','Watch_1','Hour','disp_clear_time_m',
              'rec_disp_time_m','ComplainantGender_F','ComplainantGender_M',
              'IsDrugRelated','ComplainantRace_B','ComplainantRace_L',
              'ComplainantRace_W','Division_SouthEast','ComplainantAgeRange',
              'ComplainantAge']]

distortions = []
for i in range(1, 10):
    km = KMeans(n_clusters = i,
               init='k-means++',
               n_init=10,
               max_iter=300,
               random_state=0)
    km.fit(X)
    distortions.append(km.inertia_)
    
plt.plot(range(1,10), distortions, marker='o')
plt.xlabel('Number of Clusters')
plt.ylabel('Distortion')
plt.show()

The graph above shows the distortion vs. number of clusters. This determines the number of clusters for maximum efficiency and minimum error. Based on the graph, we chose to use KMeans clustering with 3 clusters - results shown below. To note, we also tried using 4 clusters but the same results were achieved so we omitted those results.

We started by grouping similar variables into one with the rest in another, keeping our IsTheft variable as the response. Thus, X1- the first group- consists of all of the Watch categories as well as Hour to represent the time-based variables.

In [24]:
# Using KMeans
# X1 using Watch and hour
# Using number of clusters (n_clusters) from above graph

import numpy as np
import pandas as pd

X1 = df_imputed[['Watch_3','Watch_1','Watch_2','Hour']]

cls = KMeans(n_clusters=3, init='k-means++',random_state=1)
cls.fit(X1)
newfeature = cls.labels_ # the labels from kmeans clustering

y = df_imputed['IsTheft']
X = df_imputed[['disp_clear_time_m','IsDrugRelated',
                'ComplainantRace_B','ComplainantRace_L','ComplainantRace_W','ComplainantGender_F',
                'ComplainantGender_M','rec_disp_time_m','Division_SouthEast','ComplainantAgeRange',
                'ComplainantAge']]
X = np.column_stack((X,pd.get_dummies(newfeature)))

acc = cross_val_score(clf,X,y=y,cv=cv)

print ("Average accuracy (with kmeans for Watch/Variables)= ", acc.mean()*100, "+-", acc.std()*100)

Average accuracy (with kmeans for Watch/Variables)=  73.1919866247 +- 0.584401727254

The average accuracy clustering the variables above with theft is about 73% +/- 0.58. From our previous results, Watch_2 was not found to have an effect on the models generated so let's see what happens when we remove that variable:

Lastly, a slower dispatch time is also seen throughout all hours of the day (in the gold cluster at the top), starting around 4 or 5 on the rec_disp_time_m standardized value and ranges until almost 20.

    ## This includes the point itself.
params = []
for eps in [0.1, 0.125, 0.15]:

        acc = cross_val_score(clf,X,y=y,cv=cv)

        print (eps,mpts,"Average accuracy = ", acc.mean()*100, "+-", acc.std()*100)

The mini-batch kmeans algorithm is less computationally intensive than kmeans with the expense of generally slightly poorer results. This method does not recalculate the entire dataset, instead it adds the next point to the its nearest core, or center of a cluster. This faster mechanism has shown slightly decreased accuracy of results but is considered insignificant. In our case, we achieved the same result using mini-batch kmeans and kmeans.

Using the X and Y Coordinates¶

Let's try clustering with the X and Y coordinates using all the data of incidents in Dallas in 2016. Seeing how the X and Y Coordinate clusters will give us insight as to the location of incidents. We'll deploy both the DBSCAN and KMeans algorithms after using StandardScaler to normalize our variables.

In [43]:
from sklearn.cluster import DBSCAN
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from matplotlib import pyplot as plt
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler

scl_obj = StandardScaler()
scl_obj.fit(df_Plot)

data_scaled = scl_obj.transform(df_Plot) 

#data = df_Plot

cls = DBSCAN(eps=0.125, min_samples=6)
#cls = DBSCAN(eps=0.5, min_samples=5) # we are trying different parameters to see if the plot changes, but didn't have any affect.
cls.fit(data_scaled)
dbs_labels = cls.labels_ 


cls = KMeans(n_clusters=7, random_state=1)
cls.fit(data_scaled)
kmn_labels = cls.labels_

fig = plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))
title = ['DBSCAN (All Data)','KMEANS (Add Data)']

for i,l in enumerate([dbs_labels,kmn_labels]):
    
    plt.subplot(3,2,2*i+1)
    plt.scatter(data_scaled[:, 0], data_scaled[:, 1], c=l, cmap=plt.cm.rainbow, s=20, linewidths=0)
    plt.xlabel('X Coordinate'), plt.ylabel('Y Coordinate')
    plt.grid()
    plt.title(title[i])
    

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

From the figures above, we can see the vastly different results from using each algorithm for clustering the X and Y Coordinates. Using DBSCAN, most instances are clustered in a blob-like cluster with outlying points in their own clusters. It's interesting to see that this method does not distinguish any differences in the range of X and Y coordinates. In other words, it doesn't matter of X is in between -3 to 3 and Y is in between -2 and 3, the cluster encompasses a wide variety of points since it is the most dense in the middle.

Our data may be a bit too dense for DBSCAN to accurately detect more clusters. KMeans performs much better on clustering these variables. You can clearly see 7 different clusters which most likely represent the 7 different Divisions in Dallas.

scl_obj = StandardScaler()
scl_obj.fit(df_Plot_theft)

data_scaled = scl_obj.transform(df_Plot_drug) 

# DBSCAN
cls = DBSCAN(eps=0.125, min_samples=6)
cls.fit(data_scaled)
dbs_labels = cls.labels_ 

# KMeans
cls = KMeans(n_clusters=7, random_state=1)
cls.fit(data_scaled)
kmn_labels = cls.labels_

# Setup Plot parameters
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))
title = ['DBSCAN (Drug Related Data)','KMEANS (Drug Related Data)']

# Loop to create DBSCAN and KMeans plot
for i,l in enumerate([dbs_labels,kmn_labels]):
    
    plt.subplot(3,2,2*i+1)
    plt.scatter(data_scaled[:, 0], data_scaled[:, 1], c=l, cmap=plt.cm.rainbow, s=20, linewidths=0)
    plt.xlabel('X Coordinate'), plt.ylabel('Y Coordinate')
    plt.grid()
    plt.title(title[i])
    

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

Compared to previous results, DBSCAN appears to be performing better but KMeans still appears to produce the best clustering. Kmeans shows 7 different clusters again, each representing each Division. However, DBSCAN may be clustering parts of two divisions together (for example at the botton -1 to 0 location on X) but it may be showing the pattern for different geographical areas wherein a Division line does not matter. In other words, DBSCAN may be picking up that an area in a certain location sees more drug related activity in adjacent parts of 2 Divisions as compared to the other areas of those same Divisions.

Neural Network Using Keras¶

Keras is a Python library for developing deep learning models. It wraps the libraries Theano and TensorFlow and allowed us to train our Dallas Crime dataset. The dataset was split into 29 input variables (X) as shown below and the output class variable (Y) for IsTheft

We set our first layer with 12 neurons and 29 input variables. The second hidden layer was set to 8 neurons and finally, the output layer was set to 1 neuron to predict the class whether the crime IsTheft or not.

The next step was to compile our model. In this step we had to specify our properties to be used to train our network. The loss function we used was the logarithmic loss. Also, the Adam optimization was used and is usually the default algorithm used.

After compiling our model, we fit our model on our loaded data by calling the fit() function on the model. We ran 150 iterations (or epoch) and used 10 for our batch size.

Please note that we limited our model to train on 10 000 observations since our notebook kept crashing when we tried to train our whole dataset

In [11]:
# MLP in Keras
# Source: http://machinelearningmastery.com/tutorial-first-neural-network-python-keras/
from keras.models import Sequential
from keras.layers import Dense
import numpy
# fix random seed for reproducibility
numpy.random.seed(7)


# split into input (X) and output (Y) variables
df_imputed2 = df_imputed[2:10000]

y = df_imputed2['IsTheft']
x = df_imputed2 [['rec_disp_time_m','disp_clear_time_m','Hour','IsDrugRelated',
       'IsGangRelated','IsWeekend','ComplainantAgeRange',
       'ComplainantRace_A','ComplainantRace_B','ComplainantRace_C',
       'ComplainantRace_I','ComplainantRace_L','ComplainantRace_N',
       'ComplainantRace_U','ComplainantRace_W','ComplainantGender_F',
       'ComplainantGender_M','ComplainantGender_U','Division_Central',
       'Division_North Central','Division_NorthEast','Division_NorthWest',
       'Division_South Central','Division_SouthEast','Division_SouthWest',
       'Watch_1','Watch_2','Watch_3','Watch_U']]

x = np.array(x)
y = np.array(y)

# create model
model = Sequential()
model.add(Dense(12, input_dim=29, activation='relu'))
model.add(Dense(29, activation='relu'))
model.add(Dense(1, activation='sigmoid'))
# Compile model
model.compile(loss='binary_crossentropy', optimizer='adam', metrics=['accuracy'])
# Fit the model
model.fit(x, y, epochs=150, batch_size=10)
# evaluate the model
scores = model.evaluate(x, y)
print("\n%s: %.2f%%" % (model.metrics_names[1], scores[1]*100))























 

  

  







  





 




